{
  "stem": "2620.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at that time, I didn't know the difference between a soldier and an SS, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But-- or soon after, the order came out that the Jews have to wear a star.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, even before we were start wearing stars, we were neighboring with Poland-- Galicia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- they were taken away already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a lot of them escaped and came into our city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- we were hiding them, and we fed 'em, and took care of them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was like a Star of David--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--right over here--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--on-- on our coats.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I-- good question.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I know we-- we somehow, we got 'em.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How we got 'em, where we got 'em, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--we just got 'em.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it didn't feel good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was, you know, like you're being singled out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And if you, you know, if-- they can stop you any time if you don't wear 'em and they see your identification; and if you are Jewish, and you don't wear 'em you're in trouble.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, I mean, as far as I--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--know, everybody I knew wore 'em.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was-- it was sad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I-- I-- we just-- I just never did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I missed out on that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- I also stopped going to cheder, you know, which is like Hebrew school over here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I never prepared for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I never been through with it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
